{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1779183785.77316", "card_id": "Q_2040011439595861010", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 303}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价小米 YU7 GT 刷新纽北 SUV 圈速纪录，任周灿成为首个获得纽北官方圈速认证的中国车手？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 19 日，小米创办人、董事长兼 CEO 雷军宣布，小米 YU7 GT 刷新纽北 SUV 圈速纪录：7 分 34 秒 931。小米汽车首席测试车手任周灿，也成为首个获得纽北官方圈速认证的中国车手。 雷军：小米 YU7 GT 刷新纽北 SUV 圈速纪录"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-2c970f38919249e5764e2214dfdcdce5_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "486 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2040011439595861010"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI7MenkeCk+tMQEAMaCTExOTU2MzIzMCCUja/QBjAAOLMDQAByEzIwNDAwMTE0Mzk1OTU4NjEwMTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1779183785.78646", "card_id": "Q_2039464484771779756", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 180}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "新加坡总理要求民众「做好抗通胀准备」，请问 2026 年全球通胀趋势一旦确立，普通人能如何抗通胀呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "新加坡总理：中东局势或致部分经济体面临衰退风险黄循财五一群众大会讲话解读：通胀、 AI 与新新加坡精神"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f73806815d9947173253186e343a0613.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "369 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2039464484771779756"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI7M